      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing service using VAC-coated bearings and ARP hardware. The chassis dynamics are preserved via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a perfectly calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero swirl marks, while the interior Novillo leather remains taut with no bolster compression. A turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
